SUPPORT COMMUNICATION - SECURITY BULLETIN

Document ID: c04858589
Version: 1

HPSBST03517 rev.1 - HP StoreOnce Backup systems, Remote Execution of
Arbitrary Code with Privilege Elevation, Cross-Site Request Forgery (CSRF),
Cross-Site Scripting (XSS)

NOTICE: The information in this Security Bulletin should be acted upon as
soon as possible.

Release Date: 2015-12-14
Last Updated: 2015-12-14

Potential Security Impact: Remote execution of arbitrary code with privilege
elevation, cross-Site request forgery (CSRF), cross-site scripting (XSS)

Source: Hewlett Packard Enterprise, Product Security Response Team

VULNERABILITY SUMMARY
Potential security vulnerabilities have been identified with HP StoreOnce
Backup systems. The vulnerabilities could be exploited remotely resulting in
execution of arbitrary code with elevated privileges, Cross-Site Scripting
(XSS), or Cross-Site Request Forgery (CSRF).

References:

CVE-2015-5445 (CSRF)
CVE-2015-5446 (Remote Execution of Arbitrary Code with Privilege Elevation)
CVE-2015-5447 (XSS)
SSRT102090, SSRT102123, SSRT102276

SUPPORTED SOFTWARE VERSIONS*: ONLY impacted versions are listed.

  - HP StoreOnce 2610 iSCSI Backup system running HP StoreOnce Backup system
software 3.13.0 and earlier
  - BB852A: HP StoreOnce 2620 iSCSI Backup system running HP StoreOnce Backup
system software 3.13.0 and earlier
  - BB853A: HP StoreOnce 4210 iSCSI Backup system running HP StoreOnce Backup
system software 3.13.0 and earlier
  - BB854A: HP StoreOnce 4210 FC Backup system running HP StoreOnce Backup
system software 3.13.0 and earlier
  - BB855A: HP StoreOnce 4220 Backup system running HP StoreOnce Backup
system software 3.13.0 and earlier
  - BB856A: HP StoreOnce 4420 Backup system running HP StoreOnce Backup
system software 3.13.0 and earlier
  - BB857A: HP StoreOnce 4430 Backup system running HP StoreOnce Backup
system software 3.13.0 and earlier
  - BB877A: HP StoreOnce 2700 Backup running HP StoreOnce Backup system
software 3.13.0 and earlier
  - BB878A: HP StoreOnce 4500 Backup running HP StoreOnce Backup system
software 3.13.0 and earlier
  - BB879A: HP StoreOnce 4700 Backup running HP StoreOnce Backup system
software 3.13.0 and earlier
  - BB896A: HP StoreOnce 6500 Backup running HP StoreOnce Backup system
software 3.13.0 and earlier
  - BB903A: HP StoreOnce 4900 Backup running HP StoreOnce Backup system
software 3.13.0 and earlier
  - BB910A: HP StoreOnce 2900 Backup running HP StoreOnce Backup system
software 3.13.0 and earlier
  - D4T77A/AAE: HP StoreOnce VSA 4 TB 3 Year Software running HP StoreOnce
Backup system software 3.13.0 and earlier
  - D4U47A/AAE: HP StoreOnce VSA 50TB 3-year LTU/E-LTU running HP StoreOnce
Backup system software 3.13.0 and earlier
  - D4U48A/AAE: HP StoreOnce VSA 50TB 5-year LTU/E- LTU running HP StoreOnce
Backup system software 3.13.0 and earlier
  - D4U49A/AAE: HP StoreOnce VSA 4TB 5-year LTU/E-LTU running HP StoreOnce
Backup system software 3.13.0 and earlier
