The Hewlett-Packard Company thanks the following for reporting these issues
to security-alert@...com:

  - CVE-2015-5445 Tim MalcomVetter & David Odell of Optiv Security
  - CVE-2015-5447 Craig Young, Security Researcher, Tripwire VERT

RESOLUTION

HP has provided the following software update to resolve the vulnerabilities
with HP StoreOnce Backup systems.

  - HP StoreOnce Backup Software version 3.13.1

  Please find the update from the following location:

    https://h20392.www2.hpe.com/portal/swdepot/displayProductsList.do?groupNa
me=HP+StoreOnce+Backup+System+Software

